    <text type="note" xml:lang="fr" xml:id="letter-09012">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1786-03-04">1786 lе 4 Mars.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>S’il y a un dictionnaire de rime Russe imprimé, faites le acheter pour moi et envoyez le moi 
                <note type="editorial">
                In A.V. Khrapovitskii's diary under <date when-custom="1786-03-16">March 13 1786</date> stands: "Поднес первыя тетради Лексикона риѳм и получил благодарность". Khrapovitskii kept handing over books of the Rhymes' Dictionary to Catherine until <date when-custom="1786-04-21">April 21 1786</date> and was then ordered to bind all 21 books of it, which he achieved on <date when-custom="1786-04-24">April 24 1786</date> (
                <bibl>
                    <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                    , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 4-5.</biblScope>
                </bibl>
                ).
                </note>, comme les autres livres.</p>
        </body>
